    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/d30031836ec618ec018c65bbf1939e29.poster.avif?t=1771793756\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/d30031836ec618ec018c65bbf1939e29.webm?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/d30031836ec618ec018c65bbf1939e29.mp4?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你醒来时发现自己坠毁在一颗荒凉的星球上。周围只有充满敌意的荒地，被邪恶的风暴肆虐着。附近隐约可见一座孤零零的前哨站。你艰难地爬行着，在氧气即将耗尽之际，终于抵达那扇敞开的大门。门后是一条通往地下设施的斜坡。你决定进入这个设施，希望找到逃离这片诅咒之地的方法——但你并不孤单……“残渣”也与你同在。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >极致战斗体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/1bd6376ff1d876390d97fc526d00a99a.poster.avif?t=1771793756\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/1bd6376ff1d876390d97fc526d00a99a.webm?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/1bd6376ff1d876390d97fc526d00a99a.mp4?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偷偷绕过敌人以减少接触风险，运用潜行与诡计，设置陷阱或操控门禁；或选择正面交锋，使用重型武器与炸药彻底剿灭感染源。“残渣”会根据你的战术作出反应。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>高度定制化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/a722a4714eefe7e6258f2eb16cec29c0.poster.avif?t=1771793756\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/a722a4714eefe7e6258f2eb16cec29c0.webm?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/a722a4714eefe7e6258f2eb16cec29c0.mp4?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手枪、步枪、霰弹枪、重武器与炸药将组成你对抗“残渣”的武器库。升级你的装甲、武器与工具，打造你喜欢的战斗风格。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机地牢・千变万化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/e7fbf767645733812cb8d503dc5d46a2.poster.avif?t=1771793756\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/e7fbf767645733812cb8d503dc5d46a2.webm?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/e7fbf767645733812cb8d503dc5d46a2.mp4?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次探索都不尽相同，每次深入设施都将发现全新路径与秘密，引导你迈向核心。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭露隐藏的真相</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/3d9f81b50c06e6e2ec41a3fee09ace20.poster.avif?t=1771793756\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/3d9f81b50c06e6e2ec41a3fee09ace20.webm?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083940/extras/3d9f81b50c06e6e2ec41a3fee09ace20.mp4?t=1771793756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开设施的秘密，找出你为何坠落于此星球，以及“残渣”是如何入侵这里的。唯有抵达设施核心的反应堆，才能揭示其中黑暗的真相，并协助你值得信赖的伙伴——梵斯。</p>",
